import {
  Container,
  Paper,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  Chip,
  CardMedia,
  TextField,
} from "@mui/material";
import React, { useState } from "react";
import { styles } from "./styles";
const AddPostPage = () => {
  const [tagText, setTagText] = useState("");
  const handleDeleteTag = () => {};
  return (
    <Container sx={{ paddingTop: 5, paddingLeft: 2 }}>
      <Typography sx={{ fontSize: 20 }}>Add Post</Typography>
      <Paper elevation={3} sx={styles.container}>
        <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ marginLeft: 1 }}>
          <Grid item sm={6}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureName"
              label="Post Caption"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              autoFocus
              type="text"
              autoComplete="off"
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={6}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureTags"
              label="Tags"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              type="text"
              value={tagText}
            >
              <Chip>Hello</Chip>
            </TextField>
            <Chip
              label={tagText}
              sx={{ marginTop: 1 }}
              onDelete={() => {}}
            ></Chip>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={12}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureDetails"
              label="Post Details"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              type="text"
              multiline
              rows={4}
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={6}></Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default AddPostPage;
